.TH XIL\-SFX "1" "2026\-04\-19" "xil\-pipeline 0.1.8" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xil\-sfx
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xil\-sfx
[-h] (--episode EPISODE | --tag TAG) [--show SHOW] [--script SCRIPT] [--dry-run] [--max-duration MAX_DURATION] [--gen-sfx] [--gen-music] [--gen-ambience] [--sfx-music] [--local-only]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate SFX stems from an SFX config (standalone utility)

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-episode\fR \fI\,EPISODE\/\fR
Episode tag (e.g. S01E01) — derives cast and SFX config paths

.TP
\fB\-\-tag\fR \fI\,TAG\/\fR
Raw tag for non\-episodic content (e.g. V01C03, D01)

.TP
\fB\-\-show\fR \fI\,SHOW\/\fR
Show name override (default: from project.json)

.TP
\fB\-\-script\fR \fI\,SCRIPT\/\fR
Path to parsed script JSON (default: derived from cast config)

.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Preview existing vs. new stems and estimated credit cost

.TP
\fB\-\-max\-duration\fR \fI\,MAX_DURATION\/\fR
Only process effects with duration_seconds <= this value

.TP
\fB\-\-gen\-sfx\fR
Limit to SFX and BEAT entries only

.TP
\fB\-\-gen\-music\fR
Limit to MUSIC entries only

.TP
\fB\-\-gen\-ambience\fR
Limit to AMBIENCE entries only

.TP
\fB\-\-sfx\-music\fR
(deprecated) shorthand for \-\-gen\-sfx \-\-gen\-music \-\-gen\-ambience

.TP
\fB\-\-local\-only\fR
Only place stems for effects already present in SFX/; skip API generation

